Statistical Modeling in Linguistics
Roland Schäfer, Freie Universität Berlin

My CC-BY text book about GLMMs in linguistics and everything you need to
understand them. Uses the template from Language Science Press (my preferred
publisher) in an adapted form for use with knitr.

---

The Inconsolata-g font can be obtained here:
http://www.fantascienza.net/leonardo/ar/inconsolatag/inconsolata-g_font.zip

I renamed it Inconsolatar.ttf.

On Ubuntu:
sudo mkdir /usr/share/fonts/truetype/customfonts
sudo cp Inconsolatar.ttf /usr/share/fonts/truetype/customfonts/
sudo fc-cache -fv
